	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.32]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>When I bought one way back when, it was only the second one on the server I play on and cost me 45k. Now in the bazaar, I've been seeing them for about 30k, when someone does sell one. They are above 250 trivial and I know the 250 tailor who made mine had 4 attempts before making mine successfully. They're not cheap to make to begin with, then considering the failure rate on them, it's reasonable for the tailor to demand a high price to cover their overhead. <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
